{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Balancing Hope</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349850/extras/Balantica_Steam_AboutSectionBanner_Balance.gif?t=1738476537\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Managing the Hope of Two Souls</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Assigning cards to the twins adds hope to each side of the scale. If the difference in their hope grows too large, the scale will tip, and its balance will begin to falter. When the scale tips completely and balance cannot be restored, its health decreases. Additionally, failing to accumulate enough hope to surpass the set despair value for each trial also reduces the scale\u2019s health. If the scale\u2019s health is fully depleted, the journey can no longer continue.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Evolving Relationships</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After each trial, the tilt of the scale affects the twins\u2019 relationship. With strong Rapport, building hope becomes easier. In states of Conflict, it becomes much harder.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Strategically Build and Use Your Cards</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349850/extras/Balantica_Steam_AboutSectionBanner_01.gif?t=1738476537\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A Variety of Card Effects</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cards assigned to the twins do more than give hope-they offer a variety of effects. Plan your deck carefully, considering the synergies between card effects.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Exclusive Cards</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Some cards can only be assigned to one twin. Strategize your deck composition while keeping the number of exclusive cards in mind.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Choices on the Journey</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Crossroads of Dilemmas</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The path to the alter, the final destination, splits into many routes. At these crossroads, the twins will encounter various individuals and face unexpected situations.</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Forest Explorer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3349850/db75f1d4f76de23b20c48f407c5311f7493d821e.jpg"},{"name":"Desert Adventurer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3349850/e34ef19d62d3e996195b227373506160c85cbf5c.jpg"},{"name":"Mountain Conqueror","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3349850/46081409fa872a48341cf7157214d4f39d2d996b.jpg"},{"name":"End of the Journey","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3349850/3b84937a0414e1b5705bfcad24f5566845393c77.jpg"},{"name":"Unwavering Trust","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3349850/d2f7dbee98006c8a0babcd5bc13fcb4baaea9a5a.jpg"},{"name":"Uneasy Companionship","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3349850/32e129654953cefea4f2136a7ff211414c88dea9.jpg"},{"name":"Precarious Balance","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3349850/c8ad5290fe9694433d76d5871d255c9c2973f1e7.jpg"},{"name":"Recklessly Courage","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3349850/e79917de1d445f3a6d8976f6208d6248b6656d0d.jpg"},{"name":"One Turn Is Enough","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3349850/a2ea4510d00c1949a41b900d0d80a3615a118aa5.jpg"},{"name":"Stop... Stop!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3349850/511d91ef28bfa233cf843cdb935fca9a7baec451.jpg"}],"total":23},"backg